Package com.flipkart.constants

Class SQLConstants

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.constants.SQLConstants
public class SQLConstants extends Object
Contains SQL query constants for various operations related to gym management in the Flipkart system. This includes operations for gym owners, gym users, and admins.
